{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/book/2020/03/21/Functional-Light-JS.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a467f70e-c0fb-57b8-bf62-625fe74ee261","excerpt":"比较简单的一本开源书，大概算函数式编程的入门书+JavaScript 部分介绍了。 推荐章节： 第四章，为什么要减少函数参数以及柯里化，这样有利于使用 compose 函数组合步骤。 第八章，递归，利用 es6 上面的尾递归调用提高代码可读性。 附录 A，提高性能，减少运算损耗。","html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 250px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/63868/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 129.7297297297297%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/cbe2e/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.webp 148w,\n/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/1e0be/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.webp 250w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/12f09/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.png 148w,\n/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/63868/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.png 250w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/30f3f0502f4e6fafe55480e83534ed81/63868/2020-03-21-functional-light-javascript.png\"\n          alt=\"cover\"\n          title=\"cover\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">cover</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>比较简单的一本<a href=\"https://github.com/getify/Functional-Light-JS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">开源书</a>，大概算函数式编程的入门书+JavaScript 部分介绍了。</p>\n<p>推荐章节：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>第四章，为什么要减少函数参数以及柯里化，这样有利于使用 compose 函数组合步骤。</li>\n<li>第八章，递归，利用 es6 上面的尾递归调用提高代码可读性。</li>\n<li>附录 A，提高性能，减少运算损耗。</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"category":"book"},"fields":{"slug":"/book/2020/03/21/Functional-Light-JS.html","date":"March 21, 2020","title":"Functional-Light-JS"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/book/2020/03/21/Functional-Light-JS.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/03/17/Windows下面搞Cypress真的不容易.html","title":"Windows下面搞Cypress真的不容易"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/03/22/使用react-three-fiber体验美好的WebGL开发.html","title":"使用react-three-fiber体验美好的WebGL开发"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}